main event: An unidentified object was observed by a single witness in Wall Township, New Jersey, on March 30, 1966, making a 'Z' turn before disappearing.
interesting points: The sighting lasted approximately 10 minutes,The object emitted a hissing sound,The witness described the object coming out of the clouds and hovering mid-air,The object made a sharp turn and accelerated away,There are no photographs or physical evidence to support the sighting.
witness description: The observer noted the object's behavior and sound.
